sentences.sentence: Henry stands attentively, waits each time for the new wonder, emits small noises of pleasure for each Sandhill Crane,American Coot, Great Auk, Pileated Woodpecker.
sentences.translation: 亨利站在那儿聚精会神地看着，期待每一页新的神奇，当看到沙丘鹤，美洲骨顶鸡，大海雀，大啄木鸟时，他欣喜的叫了起来。
